Name: Ladybugs and Storm
About the game: Ladybugs and storm is open world exploration simulation, it is about ladybugs survival through the storm, the mission is explore the towers on tiny islands for some food, so the ladybugs will survive through the storm, there are manythings you can do in the game 1.fly on the ocean 2.fly through snow storm and rain storm 3.landing on towers for sleeping 4.search and eat some food to gain energy 5.enjoy realxing storm effect
